init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You call the number and are greeted by a woman's voice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She simply needs you to do one thing to prove your identity:

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You're about to be contacted by several people, from several different agencies.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "If you decide to join our agency, you will not be paid the typical salary.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "As you know, our country faces some unique threats-"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The rest of the call is pretty basic, and you decide to accept her offer.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've arrived at an airport hangar, and as instructed, you have come alone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The first woman you encounter is an attractive redhead.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're a prominent author, and your next book is about to hit the shelves.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: These are the two choices you have to make.
